  "page": "Great Lagoon",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:302px;\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Braavos_tvseries.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/33/Braavos_tvseries.jpg/300px-Braavos_tvseries.jpg\" width=\"300\" height=\"156\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/33/Braavos_tvseries.jpg/450px-Braavos_tvseries.jpg 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/33/Braavos_tvseries.jpg/600px-Braavos_tvseries.jpg 2x\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/index.php/File:Braavos_tvseries.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Braavos and the Great Lagoon as depicted in the television adaptation <i><a href=\"/index.php/Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"Game of Thrones\">Game of Thrones</a></i>.</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Great Lagoon</b><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwow.5B.5Bmercy_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Cmercy.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwow.5B.5Bmercy_.28the_winds_of_winter.29.7Cmercy.5D.5D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> is a lagoon northwestern <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a>. The <a href=\"/index.php/Free_Cities\" title=\"Free Cities\">Free City</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a> sits on the hundred islands within it. It is considered a bountiful fishing spot.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtwoiafthe_free_cities:_braavos.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Great_Lagoon&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracke